INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("2842", "1", "2015-01-06 10:03:56", "2015-01-06 10:03:56", "<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-7 col-md-offset-2\">\r\n<h3 style=\"color:#4A90E2\">Copyright Policy</h3>\r\nIt is Resource Room’s policy to remove any material from our site that violates copyright law or any other law. If you discover any content on ResourceRoom.ca that you believe infringes your copyright, please report this to admin@resourceroom.ca.\r\n\r\nIn order to make a valid claim, please ensure that you include the following information:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>statement that you have identified content on Resource Room that infringes your copyright or the copyright of a third party on whose behalf you are entitled to act;</li>\r\n	<li>description of the copyright work(s) that you claim have been infringed including details of the manner and extent of the alleged infringement;</li>\r\n	<li>a description of the content that you claim is infringing and the Resource Room URL(s) where such content can be located;</li>\r\n	<li>your full name, address and telephone number, a valid email address on which you can be contacted, and your Resource Room user name if you have one;</li>\r\n	<li>a statement by you that you have a good faith belief that the disputed use of the material is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law; and</li>\r\n	<li>a statement by you that the information in your notice is accurate and that you are authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the exclusive right that is allegedly infringed.</li>\r\n	<li>with respect to your statement that you are authorized to act on behalf of the owner of the exclusive right that is allegedly infringed, confirmation that such statement is made under penalty of perjury; and</li>\r\n	<li>your electronic or physical signature (which may be a scanned copy).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe will review all incoming claims and will ensure that material and content in violation of copyright or any other law is remov